'''''Cardiovirus B''''' is a species in the ''[[Cardiovirus]]'' genus and is represented by two isolates, [[Saffold virus]] (SAFV) and [[Theiler's encephalomyelitis virus|Theiler's murine encephalomyelitis virus]] (TMEV).

